#: ../../docs/changelog.rst:23 7f47cf64d6bf4812b113bb02440d0722
msgid ""
"**Redis persistence provider** вАФ optional package "
"``VibeMQ.Server.Storage.Redis``; ``RedisStorageProvider`` implements "
"``IStorageProvider`` using Redis (LIST + HASH). "
"``BrokerBuilder.UseRedisStorage(connectionString, configure)``, "
"``AddVibeMQRedisStorage(services, connectionString, configure)``, and "
"``AddVibeMQRedisStorage(services, IConfiguration)`` for config section "
"``VibeMQ:Storage:Redis`` or ``ConnectionStrings:Redis``. Options: "
"``ConnectionString``, ``Database``, ``KeyPrefix``, ``ConnectTimeoutMs``, "
"``SyncTimeoutMs``."
msgstr ""
"**–Я—А–Њ–≤–∞–є–і–µ—А –њ–µ—А—Б–Є—Б—В–µ–љ—В–љ–Њ—Б—В–Є Redis** вАФ –Њ–њ—Ж–Є–Њ–љ–∞–ї—М–љ—Л–є –њ–∞–Ї–µ—В "
"``VibeMQ.Server.Storage.Redis``; ``RedisStorageProvider`` —А–µ–∞–ї–Є–Ј—Г–µ—В "
"``IStorageProvider`` –љ–∞ Redis (LIST + HASH). "
"``BrokerBuilder.UseRedisStorage(connectionString, configure)``, "
"``AddVibeMQRedisStorage(services, connectionString, configure)`` –Є "
"``AddVibeMQRedisStorage(services, IConfiguration)`` –і–ї—П —Б–µ–Ї—Ж–Є–Є "
"–Ї–Њ–љ—Д–Є–≥—Г—А–∞—Ж–Є–Є ``VibeMQ:Storage:Redis`` –Є–ї–Є ``ConnectionStrings:Redis``. "
"–Ю–њ—Ж–Є–Є: ``ConnectionString``, ``Database``, ``KeyPrefix``, "
"``ConnectTimeoutMs``, ``SyncTimeoutMs``."

#: ../../docs/changelog.rst:24 056e858889944a59ba542dd06c9c3e38
msgid ""
"**Redis delivery durability improvements** вАФ in-flight delivery state is "
"now persisted and recovered on broker startup, so unacknowledged messages"
" are re-queued after restart. Redis purge/delete paths also use batched "
"operations to reduce round-trips."
msgstr ""
"**–£–ї—Г—З—И–µ–љ–Є—П –љ–∞–і—С–ґ–љ–Њ—Б—В–Є –і–Њ—Б—В–∞–≤–Ї–Є —Б Redis** вАФ —Б–Њ—Б—В–Њ—П–љ–Є–µ in-flight –і–Њ—Б—В–∞–≤–Ї–Є "
"—В–µ–њ–µ—А—М —Б–Њ—Е—А–∞–љ—П–µ—В—Б—П –Є –≤–Њ—Б—Б—В–∞–љ–∞–≤–ї–Є–≤–∞–µ—В—Б—П –њ—А–Є –Ј–∞–њ—Г—Б–Ї–µ –±—А–Њ–Ї–µ—А–∞, –њ–Њ—Н—В–Њ–Љ—Г "
"–љ–µ–њ–Њ–і—В–≤–µ—А–ґ–і—С–љ–љ—Л–µ —Б–Њ–Њ–±—Й–µ–љ–Є—П —Б–љ–Њ–≤–∞ —Б—В–∞–≤—П—В—Б—П –≤ –Њ—З–µ—А–µ–і—М –њ–Њ—Б–ї–µ —А–µ—Б—В–∞—А—В–∞. –Я—Г—В–Є "
"–Њ—З–Є—Б—В–Ї–Є/—Г–і–∞–ї–µ–љ–Є—П –≤ Redis —В–∞–Ї–ґ–µ –Є—Б–њ–Њ–ї—М–Ј—Г—О—В –њ–∞–Ї–µ—В–љ—Л–µ –Њ–њ–µ—А–∞—Ж–Є–Є –і–ї—П "
"—Б–Њ–Ї—А–∞—Й–µ–љ–Є—П round-trip."

