#: ../../docs/changelog.rst:35
msgid ""
"**Connection string parser fix** вАФ URL user info now correctly handles "
"percent-encoded ``:`` in usernames (e.g. ``user%3Aname``)."
msgstr ""
"**–Ш—Б–њ—А–∞–≤–ї–µ–љ–Є–µ –њ–∞—А—Б–µ—А–∞ connection string** вАФ URL user info —В–µ–њ–µ—А—М –Ї–Њ—А—А–µ–Ї—В–љ–Њ "
